instantly, letting you continue your battle in solo mode.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/960900/extras/5e4ef0a933bcc2547af9105390cfff6a.poster.avif?t=1698244535\" width=640 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/960900/extras/5e4ef0a933bcc2547af9105390cfff6a.webm?t=1698244535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/960900/extras/5e4ef0a933bcc2547af9105390cfff6a.mp4?t=1698244535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
